who is your favorite harry potter charactor and why fred and george weasley hands down they are hilarious and funny and could do outrageous things and usually get away with it i love the fact that they are not afraid of anyone but their mother i think it's sweet they alone provide me the comic relief even in the darkest times in the book they can turn even the most serious and dangerous moments funny with their witty one liners they don't seem to be affected with their lack of money they seemed invincible that is until jo rowling decided to kill fred they break rules but they set their own limit we've never been expelled have we and i have to give them standing ovation when they quit instead of being expelled by umbridge who could ever forget their great escape in book they're easy going happy go lucky but when the times call for bravery they stood up to be counted they volunteered to be harry in book they risked being on the air in potterwatch they fought in the final battle against voldemort what more could you want bravery heroism hilarity and outrageousness all rolled into two Ginny Weasley Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix Ron Weasley Fred and George Weasley Harry Potter (character) Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Magical objects in Harry Potter Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire Harry Potter: Book Seven Diagon Alley Minor characters associated with Quidditch Hermione Granger Dolores Umbridge Hogwarts Lord Voldemort Dates in Harry Potter Albus Dumbledore Order of the Phoenix Weasley family Rubeus Hagrid Harry Potter Percy Weasley Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (film) Severus Snape Neville Longbottom Sirius Black Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone Rita Skeeter Ministry of Magic Blackadder Battle of Hogwarts J. K. Rowling Molly Weasley Minor Hufflepuffs James and Lily Potter Peter Pettigrew Cho Chang Sybill Trelawney Minor Slytherins Remus Lupin Arthur Weasley Minor Ministry officials in the Harry Potter books Cliff Richard Zhao 